ize-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Branding_Panel_Files.jpg\" width=\"566\" height=\"247\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>We deliver a full brand suite with all the assets you should ever need to maintain your store\'s identity. </strong>We\'ve worked with too many pharmacies whose logos exist only as low-quality image files.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-94 size-full alignnone\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Branding_Panel_CleanUp.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>If you like your current logo, we can help you update it and turn it into a full brand. </strong>We can work backwards and develop brand guidelines around your existing logo and provide more assets to ensure flexibility while preserving recognizability. We\'ll even clean up your existing logo to make it look sharp and clean.'),(1714,95,'_triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_modal_content','field_58addcc2d58da'),(1715,95,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_title','DIGITAL DESIGN'),(1716,95,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_title','field_58a2214fd91b6'),(1717,95,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_content','Make it go to a shadowbox when you click the panel image. The shadowbox will contain information about the panel.'),(1718,95,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_content','field_58a22160d91b7'),(1719,95,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_image','62'),(1720,95,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_image','field_58a22177d91b8'),(1721,95,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_page_link',''),(1722,95,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_page_link','field_58ab5e1d6adcc'),(1723,95,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_page_link_button',''),(1724,95,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_page_link_button','field_58ab6fb4365bc'),(1725,95,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_modal_content','Make it go to a shadowbox when you click the panel image. The shadowbox will contain information about the panel.'),(1726,95,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_modal_content','field_58addcc2d58da'),(1727,95,'triptych_panel_2_triptych_pan