_Guidelines.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" /></strong>\r\n\r\nBrand guidelines help to make everything look consistent and complete. No matter how or where people interact with the pharmacy, they will have a consistent, professional experience.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-101 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Branding_Panel_Files.png\" width=\"720\" height=\"253\" />\r\n\r\nWe deliver a full brand suite with all the assets you should ever need to maintain your store\'s identity. We\'ve worked with too many pharmacies whose logos exist only as low-quality image files.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><img class=\"wp-image-94 size-full alignnone\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Branding_Panel_CleanUp.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" /></strong>\r\n\r\nWe can do as much or as little as our client wants. If they like their current logo, we can help update it. We can even work backwards and develop brand guidelines around your existing logo.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe offer free consultations to hear your story, assess your situation, and offer services to fit your needs. Our Contact page is the best way to reach us.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-100 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Panel_Signoff.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" />'),(1974,112,'_triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_modal_content','field_58addcc2d58da'),(1975,112,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_title','DIGITAL DESIGN'),(1976,112,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_title','field_58a2214fd91b6'),(1977,112,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_content',''),(1978,112,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_content','field_58a22160d91b7'),(1979,112,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_image','62'),(1980,112,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_image','field_58a22177d91b8'),(1981,112,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_page_link',''),(1982,112,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_page_link','field_58ab5e1d6adcc'),(1983,112,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_page_link_button',''),(1984,112,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_page_link_button','field_58ab6fb4365bc'),(1985,112,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_modal_content','Digital design is intended to reach as many people as possible. Visual communication must be clear, concise and attractive. It must also match your existing brand style so people immediately know who is speaking to them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-103 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Digital_Panel_Social.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" />\r\n\r\nSocial media design ensures your various channels look good, feel professional, and contribute to your brand\'s recognizability.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-105 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Digital_Panel_Email.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" />\r\n\r\nOur digital marketing design includes email layouts, web ads, and premium content offerings like infographics and e-books. We can even help with presentation design.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-106 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Digital_Panel_Photo.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" />\r\n\r\nOur studio staff also have experience in photography, videography, motion graphics, and kinetic typography. There are many different ways to share your story.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe offer free consultations to hear your story, assess your situation, and offer services to fit your needs. Our Contact page is the best way to reach us.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-100 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Panel_Signoff.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" />'),(1986,112,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_modal_content','field_58addcc2d58da'),(1987,112,'triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_title','PRINT DESIGN'),(1988,112,'_triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_title','field_58a2214fd91b6'),(1989,112,'triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_content','Make it go to a shadowbox when you click the panel image. The shadowbox will contai