" height=\"247\" />\r\n\r\nSocial media design ensures your various channels look good, feel professional, and contribute to your brand\'s recognizability.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-105 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Digital_Panel_Email.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" />\r\n\r\nOur digital marketing design includes email layouts, web ads, and premium content offerings like infographics and e-books. We can even help with presentation design.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-106 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Digital_Panel_Photo.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" />\r\n\r\nOur studio staff also have experience in photography, videography, motion graphics, and kinetic typography. There are many different ways to share your story.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe offer free consultations to hear your story, assess your situation, and offer services to fit your needs. Our Contact page is the best way to reach us.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-100 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Panel_Signoff.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"247\" />'),(2160,123,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_modal_content','field_58addcc2d58da'),(2161,123,'triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_title','PRINT DESIGN'),(2162,123,'_triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_title','field_58a2214fd91b6'),(2163,123,'triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_content','Make it go to a shadowbox when you click the panel image. The shadowbox will contain information about the panel.'),(2164,123,'_triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_content','field_58a22160d91b7'),(2165,123,'triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_image','63'),(2166,123,'_triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_image','field_58a22177d91b8'),(2167,123,'triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_page_link',''),(2168,123,'_triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_page_link','field_58ab5e1d6adcc'),(2169,123,'triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_page_link_button',''),(2170,123,'_triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_page_link_button','fie