your staff to improve processes, maximize time spent selling, and how to close deals so that both parties benefit the most.'),(2292,126,'_triptych_panel_2_triptych_panel_modal_content','field_58addcc2d58da'),(2293,126,'triptych_panel','3'),(2294,126,'_triptych_panel','field_58a22131d91b5'),(2295,127,'triptych_title',''),(2296,127,'_triptych_title','field_58a22120d91b4'),(2297,127,'triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_title','INBOUNDRX'),(2298,127,'_triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_title','field_58a2214fd91b6'),(2299,127,'triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_content','<p class=\"p1\">InboundRX is a diverse team of creators, thinkers and doers interested in making other businesses as successful as possible.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">We offer design and development services as well as a wide array of business empowerment tools.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Our specific development processes vary depending on the client and their specific needs. Do you have an idea for a project? We\'ll brainstorm with you for free if you fill out the form on this page.</p>'),(2300,127,'_triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_content','field_58a22160d91b7'),(2301,127,'triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_image',''),(2302,127,'_triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_image','field_58a22177d91b8'),(2303,127,'triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_page_link',''),(2304,127,'_triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_page_link','field_58ab5e1d6adcc'),(2305,127,'triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_page_link_button',''),(2306,127,'_triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_page_link_button','field_58ab6fb4365bc'),(2307,127,'triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_modal_content',''),(2308,127,'_triptych_panel_0_triptych_panel_modal_content','field_58addcc2d58da'),(2309,127,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_title','TALK TO US'),(2310,127,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_title','field_58a2214fd91b6'),(2311,127,'triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_content','[formidable id=\"2\"]'),(2312,127,'_triptych_panel_1_triptych_panel_content','field_58a22160d91b7'),(2313,127,'triptych_pan